# This is a monorepo -- Vercel only needs to build frontend/ (the Vite
# app). Without this, Vercel's zero-config detection scans the whole repo
# and finds backend/requirements.txt plus backend/app/api/*.py, mistakes
# it for a Python Serverless Functions setup (Vercel's own /api convention),
# and tries to pip-install fastapi/pandas/scikit-learn/etc. alongside the
# actual frontend build -- unrelated to this deployment and a likely cause
# of build failures/timeouts. The backend deploys separately on Render.
backend/
analysis/
models/
data/
reports/
slides/
docs/
